<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366466" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/B5C2CA57-2CB8-441C-B97F-70E3C0C3D6CC.jpeg?resize=1000%2C1000&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1000" height="1000" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Chidinma and Flavour come through with a new short film titled, “40yrs Lovestacle” which is inspired by their collaborative album “40 Yrs Everlasting”. The movie stars Nollywood actors, Rita Edochie, George Ezenwora & Ogechi Obilonu. The film captures the beauty of love and unity, and also details the marriage tradition in the Igbo culture. “40yrs Lovestacle” is directed by Clarence A. Peters. Watch the video below. The post Flavour & Chidinma debut Short Film “40yrs Lovestacle” starring Rita Edochie, George Ezenwora & Ogechi Obilonu | WATCH  Source: Bella Naija